{"tid":2201005,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"【求教】邊度有得賣中藥單味顆粒？","createTime":"2020-09-13T12:19:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T12:42:28.000Z","uid":232766,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b1ef917496c7cfd73fc8f6ff3eb05a9e4addf7a2","tid":2201005,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:19:26.000Z","msg":"多年前脂肪肝，朋友推介飲決明子山楂菊花茶，確實有效。<br />\n<br />\n近來又肥翻，想再飲，但又怕麻煩唔想自己「焗」，唔知邊度有得賣單味嘅中藥顆粒可以自己沖？<br />\n<br />\n我明白有啲中藥係應該只可以由醫生處方，但有啲確實無傷大雅。例如以上提到嘅決明子山楂菊花茶，3 種原料都可以輕易買到，所以照道理用顆粒都會一樣，唔會有分別，只係會方便好多。<br />\n<br />\n請問大家知唔知邊度有得賣呢啲顆粒（或者沖濟）？網上/外國都可以。謝謝！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c39fb2a6950bfd0bbd065b1b21b4f818955716","tid":2201005,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:19:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9855b571b2abcdfaa0bdd6a90f97b3319cf45c53","tid":2201005,"uid":241817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"農本方？"},{"pid":"2b2c39bff68999219523adfb117b2043b4b7b2bf","tid":2201005,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9855b571b2abcdfaa0bdd6a90f97b3319cf45c53","tid":2201005,"uid":241817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"農本方？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:22:33.000Z","msg":"好似只有複方有得散賣，單味唔可以散賣（例如我唔可以就咁買一味「山楂」），一定要經醫生處方。如有錯請指正。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83432cbc5a6e5c76bcc81acff120d82229d6d820","tid":2201005,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:27:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"87d55c5790fabf3e4eb7fc99c2eaed9134ec0030","tid":2201005,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:49:02.000Z","msg":"台灣"},{"pid":"e4fc1a1c1e4c831e09594680c9007183189fc22d","tid":2201005,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87d55c5790fabf3e4eb7fc99c2eaed9134ec0030","tid":2201005,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:49:02.000Z","msg":"台灣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:58:11.000Z","msg":"唔個可唔可以經網上買或者代購？Thanks! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ab9603b3ba0f54ae58c478c9fc24ae29d9c385","tid":2201005,"uid":298012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T13:02:32.000Z","msg":"咁要食幾多粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007296287054cfde28639b904901dc5b6f9344de","tid":2201005,"uid":4037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T13:07:52.000Z","msg":"自己買來焗啦，無得懶架，中藥顆粒垃圾來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3041db4233853d325fd66e7be8c11fbe6fcdad","tid":2201005,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6ab9603b3ba0f54ae58c478c9fc24ae29d9c385","tid":2201005,"uid":298012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T13:02:32.000Z","msg":"咁要食幾多粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T13:08:15.000Z","msg":"呢啲顆粒係沖濟，好似雀巢咖啡粉咁沖嚟飲。如果真係用嚟醫病嘅中藥，好多時都係醫生開，醫生自然會講份量（例如每次用幾多克）。但如果係啲普通食療（例如菊花茶？），其實都無咩所謂，可以自己根據個濃縮度試飲再加減。"},{"pid":"b4ca47021ac0a124cda5726fd2b643faa491f660","tid":2201005,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"007296287054cfde28639b904901dc5b6f9344de","tid":2201005,"uid":4037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T13:07:52.000Z","msg":"自己買來焗啦，無得懶架，中藥顆粒垃圾來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T13:10:15.000Z","msg":"好多人都咁講，但我以前身體有其他毛病，睇完中醫，都係用藥粉醫好。<br />\n<br />\n自己焗/煲係好，但係沖濟方便太多啦... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9486d2e89c9ecc62804035df6f7990fd22ae0283","tid":2201005,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T13:37:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e7961629b5f16aa39aaa2cc8151e58374f3a3d53","tid":2201005,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T13:39:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edcb0209539fd9bea3a63894aad97c7912920a4b","tid":2201005,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T13:44:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a3810edc6602b280d15318fa16635d79c2b29b96","tid":2201005,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T13:57:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"84c3ead473baf322627fc7d2b7cd2e70ca299ed0","tid":2201005,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T15:10:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3d382b5e565814da219cfa36f65fc8dcaaaff188","tid":2201005,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:57:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b7218a43964b8694c5fb6497e38f029e7bf4b097","tid":2201005,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9ad2d9127a94f227d1d29ba756a756d904da325c","tid":2201005,"uid":66359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T06:04:55.000Z","msg":"可以試下脂康顆粒呢隻藥"},{"pid":"bd0176599195c77e1d36a54328fcd2abf0810c17","tid":2201005,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T09:47:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"844d4c47c3d38c528a465b169fa92b60e97e0db0","tid":2201005,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T12:08:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e3a6423d588817a0ddbbff2b3fc8233822d36d74","tid":2201005,"uid":266874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T12:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1918c86fdb94bc491968d8a63741d38586b521a","tid":2201005,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"007296287054cfde28639b904901dc5b6f9344de","tid":2201005,"uid":4037,"like